  </div>

<div class="card card2">
  <div class="top">
    <img src="/assets/photos/FactoryService.jpg" alt="Timing belt service" />
    <h3>The Toy Shop Timing Belt Special</h3>
  </div>
  <p>Free timing belt with service-pay only for the labor! Includes all Toyota, Honda, Subaru, Nissan equipped with timing belts. Recommend to replace water pump with service. Only OEM parts used.</p>
</div>


<div class="card card3">
   <div class="coupon-content"> 
    <p><span class="h-4">$10&nbsp;OFF</span>Any repair or maintenance service of $100 and up.</p>
   </div>
</div>

<div class="card card4">
   <div class="coupon-content"> 
    <p><span class="h-4">$20&nbsp;OFF</span>Any repair or maintenance service of $200 and up.</p>
   </div>
</div>

<div class="card card5">
   <span class="coupon-content"> 
    <p><span class="h-4">$50&nbsp;OFF</span> Any repair or maintenance service of $600 and up.</p>
   </div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<style>
* {
  text-wrap: pretty;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

/* ---------- header styles ---------- */
.specials {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  text-align: left;
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 6rem auto;
}
@media screen and (max-width: 950px) {
  .specials {
    margin: 4rem 1rem;
  }

}

.specials-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.specials-header .line {
  flex: 1;
  height: 2px;
  background: #000;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

.specials h1 {
  font-family: "apotek-extrawide", sans-serif;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  color: #414141;
  margin: 0;
  white-space: wrap;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}

/* ---------- grid styles ---------- */

.card-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr) [col-start];
  width: 100%;
  gap: 1rem;
  justify-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.card1, .card2 {
  grid-column: span 3;

}

.card3, .card4, .card5 {
  grid-column: span 2;
}

@media screen and (max-width: 700px) {

.card {
  grid-column: span 6;
  width: 100%;
}
}

.sub {
  font-size: 50%;
}


/* ---------- top cards styles ---------- */
  .card {
    display: flex;
    position: relative;
    flex-direction: column;
    background-color: #414141;
    color: #fff;
  }
  
  .top h3,  .coupon-content, .card1 p, .card2 p {
        padding: 2rem;
  }

  div,
  img {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 150px;
    object-fit: cover;
    filter: grayscale(100%) brightness(45%);
  }

  .top h3 {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translate(0, -50%);
  }
h3, h4, .h-4 {
    font-family: "apotek-extrawide", sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #fffa92;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 1.8rem);
    line-height: 97%;
    text-align: left;
    text-wrap: balance;
}

  p {
    background-color: #414141;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 180%;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: left;
  }
</style>
